SliTaz Tiny/Touch Screen desktop
===============================================================================


The goals of the sts desktop is to provide a nice experience on realy small
screens such as 320x240 2.8" TFT or 800x480 5" HDMI/VGA. The desktop use
Openbox window manager and LXpanel. Apps are started maximized and undecored.
The top panel provide icons of opened applications and the hidden bottom panel
provide desktop switch and a close button for the current running application.

Sts can be used on any screen but was coded for custom i486/ARM flavors. These
flavors use a custom /etc/slitaz/applications.conf with sts-session as WM. Sts
can also be started by Slim or with startx and an appropriate ~/.xsession file.


===============================================================================
